headline: Wall Street Analysts Think Wynn (WYNN) Could Surge 25.54%: Read This Before Placing a Bet
summary: The average of price targets set by Wall Street analysts indicates a potential upside of 25.5% in Wynn (WYNN). While the effectiveness of this highly sought-after metric is questionable, the positive trend in earnings estimate revisions might translate into an upside in the stock.
